Two brothers. Two brothers. One sister. One 
sister. Did they go to college? No. You're the

03:40.787 --> 03:41.327
only? Younger brother. Younger brother. Where 
did he go? A&M. To A&M. And did he major in

03:47.115 --> 03:49.819
agriculture also? Dairy husbandry. Dairy 
husbandry, ah. And where did he live after he

03:54.005 --> 03:56.328
graduated? In Brenham. In Brenham. In Brenham. 
Let's see. How often did you have a date when you

04:04.713 --> 04:07.699
were a student?

04:11.886 --> 04:13.349
Didn't have many dates?

04:16.695 --> 04:22.946
When y'all had a dance, was it held in Sabeasa? And 
you had the military ball? Did y'all have the, did

04:27.753 --> 04:31.481
you have a senior dance? What were the names? What 
kinds of dances? Did they have any names? Was the

04:38.215 --> 04:40.159
cotton ball held then? That would be a big one 
later. And the ring dance?

