Now, the faculty all lived on the campus. And did 
you have a, did you, were the faculty members all

05:02.993 --> 05:10.224
good to students?

05:15.211 --> 05:15.811
Let's see. And you said you went to class 
regularly. Did you get sick ever while you were at

05:19.877 --> 05:23.702
A&M? Well, if you had, you would have remembered, I 
