11:28.092 --> 11:32.478
What effect has A&M had on your life?

11:42.090 --> 11:42.450
Yes, sir.

11:55.607 --> 11:56.007
Yes, sir.

12:10.077 --> 12:18.625
You've been among the most, if not the most, 
generous person ever, so you must have always been

12:10.077 --> 12:18.625
