When

13:44.763 --> 13:52.793
you were a student, were there any Jewish students 
at A&M then? Were there any Mexican students? And

14:00.283 --> 14:07.232
among you and your friends, did it matter that 
somebody was rich or poor? Not a bit in the world. I

14:11.594 --> 14:17.022
always thought the only thing that mattered was 
were they an Aggie or not. Yeah, that's right.

14:18.404 --> 14:18.985
Yeah, that's right.

14:23.332 --> 14:23.712
Let's see. Did you all have to polish Sully, the 
statue of Lawrence Sullivan Ross? Did you all

14:31.083 --> 14:32.546
