become?

17:42.760 --> 17:44.142
Well, it's becoming a good one. It certainly is.

17:50.991 --> 17:53.594
And I'm glad it's in the middle of the campus. And 
I'm glad that it is growing. And it's doing that

17:58.801 --> 18:01.705
thanks to people like you. it

18:03.710 --> 18:32.856
certainly is that's about all that I can think of to 
chat with you about let me thank you so much not only

